  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/44ac0bae09e493027909a385b7df8869.apng?t=1763395118\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/44ac0bae09e493027909a385b7df8869.poster.avif?t=1763395118\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=50 /></picture></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turn-based combat where every action counts. Carefully position yourself, build up and unleash your attacks at the right time!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/3f4a4cf71069468653f73f9c5a3d8dad.poster.avif?t=1763395118\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/3f4a4cf71069468653f73f9c5a3d8dad.webm?t=1763395118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/3f4a4cf71069468653f73f9c5a3d8dad.mp4?t=1763395118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your attack tiles and combo them!<br></li><li>Gain new skills and build the best deck you can before facing the Shogun.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/2f62b7ef28f5074ceb8f7d9fff9431dd.poster.avif?t=1763395118\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/2f62b7ef28f5074ceb8f7d9fff9431dd.webm?t=1763395118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2084000/extras/2f62b7ef28f5074ceb8f7d9fff9431dd.mp4?t=1763395118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>